♦ Set Light Potion Box weight to 1
  - Must not be openable if the weight will exceed weight capacity or cause 90% weight
♦ Set Light Potion weight to 3:
  - Light White Potion
  - Light Blue Potion

♦ Set Elite Siege Potion Box weight to 1 (both I and II)
  - Must not be openable if the weight will exceed weight capacity or cause 90% weight
♦ Set Siege Potion weight to 10:
  - Siege White Potion
  - Siege Blue Potion
